# UI Theme and Design System

- Colors
  - Primary `#0057b7`, Secondary `#28A745`, Background `#fafafa`, Text `#272727`.
  - Map these to CSS variables in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) and ensure shadcn tokens use them.

- Typography
  - Prefer Gilroy; fallback to system fonts/Arial if Gilroy is unavailable.
  - Declare font variables in `:root` and apply on `html`/`body` in [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx).

- Components
  - Use shadcn/ui primitives. Keep spacing, radius, and shadows consistent via Tailwind tokens.
  - Buttons: primary = solid primary color; secondary = outline with secondary accents.

